    "timing_status": "estimated"
  },
  {
    "voice_id": "sb_v04",
    "section": "doctrine",
    "text": "斯多葛主义最核心的一步，不是压住情绪，而是先切开两层：外界发生了什么，和我准备怎么解释它。",
    "target_duration_sec": 9.0,
    "intended_pause_after_sec": 0.25,
    "emphasis_words": ["两层", "解释它"],
    "visual_section_id": "s04",
    "timing_status": "estimated"
  },
  {
    "voice_id": "sb_v05",
    "section": "method",
    "text": "在你准备回复、争辩、证明自己之前，先停一秒。",
    "target_duration_sec": 5.4,
    "intended_pause_after_sec": 0.35,
    "emphasis_words": ["先停一秒"],
    "visual_section_id": "s05",
    "timing_status": "estimated"
  },
  {
    "voice_id": "sb_v06",
    "section": "method",
    "text": "问一句：这件事，到底属于我能控制的部分吗？",
    "target_duration_sec": 5.2,
